Program: Omnibus
Title: Stalking
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376l9f
Last Broadcast Date: 15 August 1996
Explaining stalkers, analysing the reasons behind obsessive attachments and looking at the effects on the people being stalked. Includes a look at the case of Tracy Sant whose stalker was the first person to be jailed under anti-stalking laws.